1
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,360
<i>From now on,</i>

2
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:27,320
<i>Bandit Pan will assist me</i>
<i>in running this farm.</i>

3
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,600
<i>Are you okay with that, Auntie?</i>

4
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,880
Mr. Yai!

5
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:37,800
<i>Swear to this statue</i>
<i>that you will never betray Madam</i>

6
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:41,000
by siding with
or helping Yai in harming her.

7
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:43,320
Otherwise, all ties between us

8
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,320
will be severed from now on.

9
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:06,200
Can't you let me have
some peace of mind for once? Huh?

10
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,120
You're too infatuated with her.

11
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,480
Because she makes me happy.

12
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,520
And you?

13
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:16,040
<i>You were born only to give me pain!</i>

14
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,800
Huh?

15
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,160
Mr. Yai?

16
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,440
Who's that? Let's go, Kan.

17
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,840
Don't shoot, Mr. Yai.

18
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,400
Oh. It's you, Piak?

19
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,120
It's me.

20
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,480
Someone was hiding
and trying to shoot you.

21
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,000
This isn't a joke anymore.

22
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,760
It's a life-and-death situation.

23
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,720
If Piak hadn't noticed,

24
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,760
I'd be organizing your funeral right now.

25
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,640
And did he say who it was?

26
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,720
I just saw them briefly.

27
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,840
Must be Teera's men.

28
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,880
So how can you still be so calm?

29
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:40,120
You should regroup outside
and come up with a plan.

30
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,240
Just one misstep,

31
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,240
and the farm will fall into their hands.

32
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:47,680
I didn't come back
because I wanted Dad's stupid inheritance.

33
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,160
Do something for me.

34
00:06:56,680 --> 00:07:00,320
Go to the hospital,
and get all my father's medical records.

35
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,600
Got it.

36
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:12,440
I want to hear that he's dead,
not the word "sorry".

37
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,360
You idiots.

38
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,480
I'm sorry.

39
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,680
Piak saved him in time, Boss.

40
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,680
I didn't expect him to show up.

41
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,400
Get out.

42
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,640
- I'm sorry.
- You idiot.

43
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,560
Go.

44
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:37,200
They're all bad at their jobs.

45
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,200
Where are you going?

46
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,480
To get some help.

47
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,600
Business negotiation?

48
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:59,360
Did you forget
that you still owe me money?

49
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:01,960
I'll definitely pay back the debt.

50
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:05,600
But I'd like to invite you
to invest a little more,

51
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:08,400
and you'll see your profits
multiply many times over.

52
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,960
How? Tell me.

53
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:20,280
The son of the owner
of Paisal Farm has returned.

54
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,000
So what?

55
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:27,600
He killed a farm worker
and then fled the scene.

56
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:31,000
Now, he has become a bandit

57
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:33,039
and has come back to threaten me.

58
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:36,559
So I need some men to handle him.

59
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,600
If you could help me,

60
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,919
ten percent of the inheritance

61
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,960
will be transferred
to your account immediately.

62
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,520
Are you done?

63
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,960
Because if you don't stop talking…

64
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,040
Hey.

65
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,800
Put a bullet in each of them.

66
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,960
Hey, wait, wait.

67
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,320
Mr. Tong.

68
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,160
Let's talk nicely.

69
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:00,360
Fifty percent, then.

70
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:10,320
And I'll also let you have someone.

71
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:14,800
I guarantee she's much hotter
than the ones in the pictures you saved.

72
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:25,800
Mom, please come out and eat.

73
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:28,680
I've warmed up the meal for you,
so you can take your medicine.

74
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,240
Pin.

75
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:37,040
Why didn't you answer my calls?

76
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,600
I was cooking for my mom. What's up?

77
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,840
Madam called and asked you

78
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:47,160
to bring the shoulder bag
from her desk drawer to her right now.

79
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,520
She forgot to bring it with her.

80
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:51,560
And she also
specifically asked for you, Pin.

81
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:53,360
She doesn't trust anyone else.

82
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,840
She's probably worried
about losing the money inside.

83
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,840
And where is she now?

84
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,400
Hold up, Hold up. Wait.

85
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,480
Where are you going?

86
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,400
Madam asked me
to bring something to her in town.

87
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,680
Good. I have a business there too.

88
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:35,360
But I'm in a hurry.

89
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:37,360
Can't you ride there yourself, Mr. Yai?

90
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:40,200
My bike broke down. Why not?

91
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:42,000
Can't I just tag along?

92
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,120
Do you really have to be mean to me?

93
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,400
Let's go.

94
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,680
Where should I drop you off?

95
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,960
I'll get off wherever you go.

96
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,080
I'm here to buy something from this shop.

97
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:38,160
Great. Then I'll get off here.

98
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,280
Thanks for the ride.

99
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:31,360
This way.

100
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,800
Where's Madam?

101
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:40,840
Madam Krongsuk fainted,
so the boss opened a room for her to rest.

102
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,920
Is she okay?

103
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,000
She's in here.

104
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,560
I don't see Madam in here.

105
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:08,920
Open the door.

106
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:26,960
Hey, what are we supposed to tell her mom?

107
00:13:27,560 --> 00:13:30,480
Tell her I asked Pin to bring me some food

108
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,960
because I was hungry.

109
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,440
Go drive.

110
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:40,160
Take this.

111
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:43,160
Don't think
I don't know what's on your mind.

112
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:46,360
Go drive.

113
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:53,200
Open the door right now.

114
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:56,160
Open the door.

115
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:13,120
We meet again.

116
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:16,160
It's clearly fate.

117
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:19,960
Who are you? We've never met before.

118
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:21,800
And where's Madam?

119
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:25,400
You've gone to get a loan from my company.

120
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:27,160
If you're in financial trouble,

121
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,360
just become my wife.

122
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:32,200
I, Mr. Tong, pay quickly.

123
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:34,120
Your pockets will never be empty.

124
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:44,040
Madam! Please help me, Madam!

125
00:14:44,640 --> 00:14:47,160
Madam! Manager!

126
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,600
Help me! Madam!

127
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:50,800
- Madam!
- Come here.

128
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:53,800
Those two couldn't even save themselves.

129
00:14:53,880 --> 00:14:55,680
How are they supposed to help you?

130
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,280
Sir,

131
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:02,680
sexual harassment is a serious offense
which carries harsh punishments.

132
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:05,560
You'd be in prison for life.

133
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:08,040
Society would condemn you.

134
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:11,840
And you'd have no place
in society anymore, sir.

135
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:17,200
You know what? My money

136
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:20,160
can definitely keep you
and your mother quiet.

137
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,240
So I'm not afraid.

138
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:38,560
Damn it.

139
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:42,600
Come out!

140
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:44,960
Hey! Open the door.

141
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:46,960
Open the door! Pin!

142
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,360
You think you're safe in there?

143
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:51,840
You're so tough, huh? Come out.

144
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,000
- Huh?
- Hey.

145
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,160
- Who cut the power?
- Hey.

146
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,800
What the hell?

147
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,880
- Who cut the power?
- What happened?

148
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,640
- Is this a police raid?
- What?

149
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,320
- Why are the lights out?
- Huh?

150
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:15,160
- Is it the police?
- Let's go.

151
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:21,120
What the hell is going on?

152
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,960
Hey! Hey!

153
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,400
Where are they?

154
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:29,720
Why are the lights out? Is it the police?

155
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:31,080
No, Boss.

156
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:33,600
Then check the circuit breaker, you idiot.

157
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:34,680
Yes, Boss.

158
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,440
Pin.

159
00:16:48,520 --> 00:16:50,720
Open the door, Pin. Pin.

160
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:07,040
Pin? Pin.

161
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:09,640
Mr. Yai…

162
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:13,800
Mr. Yai…

163
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:15,839
I'm scared, Mr. Yai.

164
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,400
I'm scared…

165
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:51,000
Madam asked me to come here.

166
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:53,920
- But I didn't know where she…
- Pin. Pin. No need to say anything.

167
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,760
Let's get out of here. Now.

168
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:57,240
Come on.

169
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:03,800
- Come.
- Hey!

170
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,800
Run, Pin. Run.

171
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,880
- Hey!
- Hey.

172
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:08,920
Where are you going?

173
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:20,080
- Give me that.
- Hey.

174
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:28,360
Boss, this is the scumbag who cheated
and stole from our gambling den last time.

175
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:34,080
I searched the entire city for you,

176
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:36,120
and now you're trapped here.

177
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:38,320
The devil is helping us.

178
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:42,240
If you and I are going
to sort out our issues,

179
00:18:42,320 --> 00:18:44,440
there's no need
for a woman to get involved.

180
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:46,840
Let Pinanong go, then we'll settle things.

181
00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:49,840
Big words for the one who's about to die.

182
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,680
You're still negotiating?

183
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,200
Huh?!

184
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:54,720
- Don't hurt Mr. Yai!
- Come here.

185
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:55,960
- Ah.
- No.

186
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,000
Mr. Yai!

187
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,040
You're so tough, huh?

188
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:05,880
- Still tough now? Huh?
- Mr. Yai!

189
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,320
Well?

190
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:14,320
Come at me. Get up.

191
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,120
Hey.

192
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:32,480
Come here.

193
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,560
I told you not to hurt Pin!

194
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,840
- Let go of him!
- Let go!

195
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,600
You! Let go!

196
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,400
Let go of him!

197
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:55,160
Hey! Let go!

198
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:04,080
Mr. Yai.

199
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:13,400
Mr. Yai.

200
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:19,040
This is getting out of hand.

201
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,840
Did they really sneak in to shoot people?

202
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:22,000
Yes.

203
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,880
Are you sure
you weren't just seeing things?

204
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,360
Your eyesight isn't that good.

205
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:27,120
Ugh. You don't believe what your man said?

206
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,640
Go ask Mr. Yai yourself then.

207
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:30,960
Then let's go.

208
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:32,480
Split up and find them.

209
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,360
I'll go get the gun.

210
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,280
Yes.

211
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,320
Hey. Jom.

212
00:20:39,560 --> 00:20:40,560
Didn't you hear me?

213
00:20:41,840 --> 00:20:43,560
Why are you so worried?

214
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:45,880
It was just his enemies
settling a score with him.

215
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,720
Your Mr. Yai isn't an ordinary guy.

216
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:49,720
But this is our farm.

217
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:52,120
Anyone's enemy
has no right to come in here.

218
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:55,560
Let's go, Piak. Forget about him.

219
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:59,000
You're not going?

220
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:04,520
Where are those guys going?

221
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:06,280
Aren't they going to work?

222
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:10,560
A scumbag just returned to the farm,
and he brought other bad guys with him.

223
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:12,320
Hey. I asked nicely.

224
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,520
Why do you have to mess with me?

225
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,480
Hey, hey.

226
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:18,760
Don't do it. Don't say I didn't warn you.

227
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:21,440
Hey.

228
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:25,240
What? You think
those muscles make you so tough?

229
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:29,720
It's brains over brawn now. Come on.

230
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,880
Not so tough, huh?

231
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:36,080
Hey, stop right there.

232
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:37,560
‪Wanna end up in the slaughterhouse?

233
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:52,560
Mr. Yai.

234
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:56,360
Mr. Yai. Mr. Yai.

235
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:01,400
Does it hurt a lot, Mr. Yai?

236
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:16,080
Mr. Yai. Are you in a lot of pain?

237
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:18,640
It was all because of me.

238
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:20,800
I'm the reason you got hurt.

239
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:24,520
Just forget it. What about you, Pin?

240
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:26,760
Are you okay?

241
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:29,480
Did that bastard do anything to you?

242
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:32,240
No.

243
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:35,080
They locked us in here.

244
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:38,480
What are we going to do?

245
00:22:51,360 --> 00:22:54,520
Looking at how this is turning out,
I probably won't survive.

246
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:56,520
But for you…

247
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:02,240
I'll tell Tong before I die

248
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:06,320
that there's really nothing going on
between you and me.

249
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:11,280
He likes you,
so he'll definitely keep you alive.

250
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:15,720
No, I won't let you do it that way.

251
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:18,280
Or do you really want something
to happen between us?

252
00:23:19,760 --> 00:23:23,480
Uh, it's not like that.

253
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:26,200
I mean…

254
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:29,760
I'd never leave you behind
to save my own skin.

255
00:23:31,120 --> 00:23:33,440
I'd rather die with you

256
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:36,480
than become his woman.

257
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:52,440
You're crying again.

258
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:01,960
I just feel bad for you.

259
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:06,920
They were all beating you up,

260
00:24:07,560 --> 00:24:09,640
and I was afraid you would die.

261
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:16,440
Does it hurt a lot?

262
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,880
- I'm sorry.
- We're not going to die.

263
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:30,440
Reach your hand inside my jeans.

264
00:24:31,120 --> 00:24:31,960
Huh?

265
00:24:33,040 --> 00:24:36,320
Uh, what did you just say?

266
00:24:37,080 --> 00:24:39,000
Reach in? Reach in what?

267
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:41,640
Just do it, and you'll see.

268
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:45,720
This isn't the time to tease me, Mr. Yai.

269
00:24:47,560 --> 00:24:49,880
Hey, I can't reach my phone with my hand.

270
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:52,760
I hid it in the waistband of my underwear.

271
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:00,280
This is life-or-death.

272
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:02,200
I wouldn't think of doing anything lewd.

273
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:06,960
Hurry up. Do it before they come back.

274
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,080
Hurry, Pin.

275
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:13,120
Do it. Hurry.

276
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:17,160
Wait a sec.

277
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:20,320
- It's sliding down. Hurry, reach in.
- Okay, okay.

278
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:24,080
Hurry.

279
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:29,160
Just do it. Reach in. Go.

280
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:32,760
Pin. Lower.

281
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:35,760
Pin, go lower.

282
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:38,600
A little lower.

283
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,360
Ugh.

284
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,520
Even lower.

285
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,320
Lower.

286
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,360
- Where is it?
- Oh.

287
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:54,280
That's not it, Pin. You went too low.

288
00:25:57,040 --> 00:25:57,880
Huh?

289
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,680
Huh?

290
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:10,000
Are you messing with me now?

291
00:26:10,080 --> 00:26:11,120
Oh?

292
00:26:13,080 --> 00:26:14,320
- Huh?
- I'm not.

293
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:19,280
A little to the left.

294
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:21,240
Have you found it yet? The hard spot.

295
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:22,760
Found it yet?

296
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,080
Yeah, take it out.

297
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:33,440
I'll call the police.

298
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:36,200
Hey, wait.

299
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:38,400
Dial the number I tell you to.

300
00:27:00,040 --> 00:27:02,480
Yai, I'm going crazy
with every passing day.

301
00:27:02,560 --> 00:27:03,920
Where are you?

302
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:08,360
Listen carefully. I'm being held.

303
00:27:09,120 --> 00:27:11,240
Being held? You deserved it.

304
00:27:11,320 --> 00:27:12,160
Huh?

305
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,280
Being held by whom?

306
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:17,960
Tell Uncle Pload I urgently need help,

307
00:27:18,040 --> 00:27:21,080
and tell him to use the Ghost Guardian
protocol at Chomphon Cave.

308
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,160
Remember that.

309
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:24,600
The Ghost Guardian protocol
at Chomphon Cave.

310
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:26,520
The Ghost Guardian protocol
at Chomphon Cave.

311
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:30,640
Pin, hide it.

312
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:32,000
Lie down now. Hurry.

313
00:27:33,040 --> 00:27:33,880
Huh?

314
00:27:35,120 --> 00:27:36,080
Yai.

315
00:27:52,040 --> 00:27:53,320
Turn off the phone and hide it.

316
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:55,800
Turn it off and hide it.

317
00:27:56,320 --> 00:27:57,720
Stuff it in. Yeah.

318
00:27:58,240 --> 00:27:59,720
Yeah, uh-huh.

319
00:28:06,840 --> 00:28:10,120
You're about to die,
and you're still in the mood for that?

320
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:14,040
Well, how could I not be?

321
00:28:14,120 --> 00:28:15,480
My girl is this beautiful.

322
00:28:15,560 --> 00:28:17,120
I'd need a proper goodbye.

323
00:28:19,040 --> 00:28:19,880
Hey.

324
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:22,320
Get up.

325
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:25,440
Come here. Up.

326
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,440
- Go.
- Let's go.

327
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:53,920
Where are you going?

328
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:58,400
And what does that have to do with you?

329
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:00,160
Why wouldn't it have to do with me?

330
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:03,200
This pickup truck belongs to the farm.

331
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:05,080
That means it belongs to Mr. Yai.

332
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:07,600
You need permission to drive it anywhere.

333
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,720
I'm just going shopping.

334
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,320
I don't think so

335
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:16,200
With that suitcase,

336
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,120
I think you're trying to run away.

337
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:23,560
Hey. Hey.

338
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,840
Hey, where are you going?

339
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,680
- Let go of me!
- Give me the key. Give it.

340
00:29:26,760 --> 00:29:28,840
- Hey.
- Ouch.

341
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:33,160
You slapped me? How about I kiss you back?

342
00:29:38,520 --> 00:29:40,080
She sure slaps hard.

343
00:29:40,800 --> 00:29:42,320
We'll settle it later.

344
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:54,160
I was right
to ask for your help, Mr. Tong.

345
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:57,000
This is a win-win situation.

346
00:29:58,120 --> 00:30:00,920
Okay, I'll be waiting for the good news.

347
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:07,520
Yai really went to help Pin.

348
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:09,440
Do you see now, Teera?

349
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:12,160
Pin isn't as innocent as she appears.

350
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:19,040
And what will Mr. Tong do to those two?

351
00:30:19,840 --> 00:30:22,200
No idea. I don't care.

352
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:26,120
I just want Yai out of my life.

353
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:29,200
Let me look
at the money we traded Pin for.

354
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:36,160
Auntie. Auntie.

355
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:38,840
Pan stole a pickup truck and drove away.

356
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:40,520
And he tried to harass me too.

357
00:30:40,600 --> 00:30:43,240
I can't stand
being around these thugs anymore.

358
00:30:44,560 --> 00:30:46,440
Huh? Money?

359
00:30:46,520 --> 00:30:48,120
- Why is there so much money?!
- Hey.

360
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:53,720
Where did you get this money from?

361
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:56,200
From gambling again?

362
00:30:57,000 --> 00:31:00,360
You don't need to know where it came from.

363
00:31:01,120 --> 00:31:04,720
Just know that from now on,

364
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:06,360
you won't see Yai again,

365
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,880
because tonight,

366
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:11,120
someone will send him to Hell.

367
00:31:12,360 --> 00:31:13,680
As for Pan,

368
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:16,880
you can just report him to the police
for trying to harass you.

369
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:19,360
That's all we need to do
to get rid of him.

370
00:31:19,440 --> 00:31:20,560
Happy ending.

371
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:24,720
What did you mean by "send him to Hell"?

372
00:31:42,920 --> 00:31:43,880
Here.

373
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:46,280
Take this money to buy whatever you want,

374
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:48,760
and zip your mouth.

375
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:54,840
If I could just have another 200,000,

376
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:58,120
I'd completely erase it from my brain.

377
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:25,200
May you and her be together
in the same grave

378
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:29,200
until the end of time,
Mr. Chalit and Pinanong.

379
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,040
Hey.

380
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:36,760
Go. Get in. Go.

381
00:32:38,520 --> 00:32:39,560
Go.

382
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,120
Hey.

383
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:02,200
We only have four hours.

384
00:33:02,280 --> 00:33:04,840
We'll go to Phetchaburi by jetboat.

385
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,680
My son, Pan, is waiting there.

386
00:33:07,280 --> 00:33:10,200
Then we'll head
to Chomphon Cave in Ratchaburi.

387
00:33:10,280 --> 00:33:12,960
We have to get there in time. Let's go.

388
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:13,960
Pload.

389
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:16,080
Hey, hey.

390
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,520
Wait a minute.

391
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,680
Pen, don't try to stop me.

392
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:26,000
You shouldn't have trusted Pan.

393
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:28,120
If anything happens to Mr. Yai,

394
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:30,680
I will never forgive myself.

395
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:35,320
I'm not stopping you, but I'm telling you

396
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:37,240
to be careful.

397
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:38,720
Okay?

398
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,760
Thank you.

399
00:33:41,840 --> 00:33:42,920
Let's go.

400
00:33:43,760 --> 00:33:44,920
Take care of each other.

401
00:34:36,679 --> 00:34:38,840
I have stolen valuables

402
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:41,320
that could be sold for tens of thousands.

403
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:46,639
But how many of you guys are there?

404
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,360
Eight ways?

405
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:49,840
That split is going to be pathetic.

406
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:54,080
Are you trying to pit us
against each other?

407
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:57,120
I have a hidden chest
full of stolen goods.

408
00:34:58,640 --> 00:34:59,840
If you guys want to split it,

409
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:04,080
you'd be well off
for the rest of your lives.

410
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:06,000
You think you can fool me?

411
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:07,440
Thirty-seventy.

412
00:35:08,080 --> 00:35:09,800
I'll give you guys seventy.

413
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,440
If I'm lying,

414
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:14,440
you guys can still shoot me.

415
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:55,000
Yai, go in there with me.

416
00:35:55,600 --> 00:35:57,440
You guys keep an eye on Pin.

417
00:35:59,080 --> 00:36:00,720
If you mess with me,

418
00:36:01,640 --> 00:36:02,920
consider Pin dead.

419
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:06,200
Sun, watch my back.

420
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:08,040
Let's go.

421
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,320
Mr. Yai.

422
00:36:14,240 --> 00:36:17,320
Don't cry, Pin. I'm not going in to die.

423
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:23,920
Remember, I will never leave you.

424
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:30,080
Enough of this nonsense. Go.

425
00:36:33,120 --> 00:36:34,960
I'll be waiting for you, Mr. Yai.

426
00:36:46,080 --> 00:36:48,080
Go. Walk.

427
00:37:25,080 --> 00:37:28,480
Hey, stand down. A woman's there too.

428
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:37,280
Pan, who's that woman?

429
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:44,920
She must be Pinanong, Dad.

430
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:46,680
Aunt Unreuan's daughter.

431
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:49,000
Yai went to save her
at Mr. Tong's gambling den.

432
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:52,000
Oh, Pinanong?

433
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:55,280
Guys. Stand down for now.

434
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:57,240
Pinanong's gonna get caught
in the crossfire.

435
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:18,800
Hey, are we there yet?

436
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:20,520
Where's the hidden chest you mentioned?

437
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:23,280
Don't rush me. The path is slippery.

438
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,520
I can't even balance myself,

439
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:26,720
being handcuffed behind my back like this.

440
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:27,840
If I was handcuffed on the front,

441
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:29,440
we would have reached
the hiding spot by now.

442
00:38:30,040 --> 00:38:32,120
The longer we take,
the more dangerous it becomes.

443
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:34,280
Once the water floods in,

444
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:37,320
we'll be swimming instead of walking.

445
00:38:37,920 --> 00:38:39,600
Hmm? What do we do?

446
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:42,600
Sun. Uncuff him.

447
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:51,120
- Hold it at the front.
- Hey.

448
00:38:52,120 --> 00:38:53,440
Slowly.

449
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:55,640
I won't miss

450
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,600
at this distance.

451
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:30,920
You…

452
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,680
Hey, what's taking them so long?

453
00:39:53,160 --> 00:39:56,240
Watch the woman. You, follow me.

454
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:57,160
Yes.

455
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:11,120
Hey.

456
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:39,080
Hey.

457
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:51,600
Damn it.

458
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:05,440
- Yai played us.
- Huh?

459
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,760
Kill her right now.

460
00:41:14,920 --> 00:41:16,600
- Huh?
- Hey. What the hell?

461
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:18,840
- Hey.
- What's this smoke?

462
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:21,000
What the hell?

463
00:41:21,080 --> 00:41:22,800
I can't breathe.

464
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:27,960
Where did they come from?

465
00:41:28,040 --> 00:41:29,200
You!

466
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:35,320
Go!

467
00:41:37,200 --> 00:41:39,080
Keep an eye on her.

468
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:40,200
I'll go in to help Mr. Yai.

469
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:42,560
- Yes, Dad.
- Mr. Yai…

470
00:41:42,640 --> 00:41:44,800
- Pin.
- Hey, let go of me! Let go.

471
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:47,160
- Pin, stay here.
- Let go. Let me go.

472
00:41:47,240 --> 00:41:48,960
- You thugs, let me go.
- Come here, Pin.

473
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:50,480
- Don't go in there.
- Mr. Yai.

474
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:51,720
- Go.
- Mr. Yai!

475
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:53,440
- Stay here.
- Let me go.

476
00:41:53,520 --> 00:41:54,600
- Mr. Yai!
- Pin, come here.

477
00:42:11,200 --> 00:42:12,400
Mr. Yai, heads up!

478
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:20,320
- You…
- No, Uncle Pload.

479
00:42:32,560 --> 00:42:34,360
We've taken care
of everything outside, Mr. Yai.

480
00:42:35,040 --> 00:42:36,280
Did you kill anyone?

481
00:42:36,360 --> 00:42:39,280
Just bruises and wounds, no one dead.

482
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,400
Alright.

483
00:42:42,480 --> 00:42:44,320
You guys tie these three up.

484
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:49,480
Did you get shot, Mr. Yai?

485
00:42:54,720 --> 00:42:57,520
- Let go of me. Let me go!
- Don't be so stubborn.

486
00:42:57,600 --> 00:42:58,840
- Don't resist!
- Hey.

487
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:02,760
- Let go!
- Hey, Pin! Pin!

488
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,280
Pin, calm down. Easy.

489
00:43:04,360 --> 00:43:05,360
Don't you remember me?

490
00:43:07,360 --> 00:43:08,400
It's Pan,

491
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:11,520
Yai's sidekick
who's been following him around.

492
00:43:12,560 --> 00:43:13,480
Pan?

493
00:43:13,560 --> 00:43:15,400
Yeah, it's me.

494
00:43:16,120 --> 00:43:17,400
That's Pan, Uncle Pload's son.

495
00:43:18,720 --> 00:43:21,800
Uncle Pload was the head worker
when my dad was still alive.

496
00:43:21,880 --> 00:43:22,880
Don't you remember?

497
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:24,760
Mr. Yai?

498
00:43:26,080 --> 00:43:27,080
Mr. Yai.

499
00:43:27,960 --> 00:43:29,080
Are you hurt?

500
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:32,120
I'm okay, Pin.

501
00:43:32,200 --> 00:43:33,680
How can you be okay?

502
00:43:33,760 --> 00:43:35,200
You're bleeding so much.

503
00:43:35,840 --> 00:43:37,120
Please help him.

504
00:43:37,200 --> 00:43:38,520
- Take him to a doctor.
- Hey, hey.

505
00:43:38,600 --> 00:43:40,360
- You have to be okay.
- Mr. Yai.

506
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:42,000
- Phong, come help him.
- Mr. Yai.

507
00:43:42,080 --> 00:43:43,120
- Hey, hey, Pan.
- Dad.

508
00:43:43,200 --> 00:43:44,320
- Help Yai, Dad.
- Hey.

509
00:43:44,400 --> 00:43:46,720
- It's none of your business. Come here.
- Mr. Yai.

510
00:43:46,800 --> 00:43:47,640
The blood.

511
00:43:47,720 --> 00:43:49,160
Don't butt in.

512
00:43:49,240 --> 00:43:50,560
- Huh?
- Stay here.

513
00:43:50,640 --> 00:43:51,920
- Mr. Yai.
- Phong.

514
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:56,280
Get every one of these scumbags
into the cave. Go.

515
00:43:56,360 --> 00:43:57,200
Yes, Boss.

516
00:43:57,280 --> 00:43:59,480
And you, come with me. Come.

517
00:43:59,560 --> 00:44:01,520
- But Dad, Yai is… Dad!
- Stop it.

518
00:44:03,360 --> 00:44:04,560
- Dad.
- Come here.

519
00:44:04,640 --> 00:44:06,960
- Don't get in the way, Pan.
- Yai.

520
00:44:07,040 --> 00:44:07,880
Hey.

521
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:09,840
What?

522
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:11,840
Dad.

523
00:44:11,920 --> 00:44:14,000
Why aren't we rushing Yai to the hospital?

524
00:44:15,000 --> 00:44:18,240
Mr. Yai isn't a weakling like you, Pan.

525
00:44:19,360 --> 00:44:22,720
But you need to tell me

526
00:44:22,800 --> 00:44:26,240
everything that happened
at the farm before this.

527
00:44:32,600 --> 00:44:34,840
Oh, Mr. Yai.

528
00:44:34,920 --> 00:44:37,880
Hang in there, Mr. Yai. You'll be okay.

529
00:44:39,720 --> 00:44:43,080
I thought you'd be happy if I just died.

530
00:44:45,080 --> 00:44:46,840
I'm not a monster, you know.

531
00:44:47,520 --> 00:44:49,720
Come here.
We need to stop the bleeding first.

532
00:44:49,800 --> 00:44:51,440
Let me take a look at the wound.

533
00:44:51,520 --> 00:44:53,880
But your madam hates me.

534
00:44:53,960 --> 00:44:57,320
If she wanted me dead,
would you dare disobey her orders?

535
00:45:01,040 --> 00:45:03,480
I will make her stop hating you.

536
00:45:05,440 --> 00:45:06,560
I mean it.

537
00:45:09,640 --> 00:45:11,120
Mr. Yai.

538
00:45:11,200 --> 00:45:13,560
Slowly, Pin. Be gentle.

539
00:45:17,880 --> 00:45:19,240
I don't see any wounds.

540
00:45:21,200 --> 00:45:22,880
Oh, really?

541
00:45:23,720 --> 00:45:24,600
No wounds?

542
00:45:24,680 --> 00:45:26,240
Then,

543
00:45:26,320 --> 00:45:28,720
it must be the blood of Tong's henchmen.

